    public class BlockSanguinaryPedestal
extends org.cyclops.cyclopscore.block.BlockTile
implements IBlockRarityProvider, IBlockTank
    Pedestal that can obtain blood from blood stained blocks and can optionally extract blood from mobs when a blood extractor is inserted.
